snippet.textDisplay: This one's from Fischer, she really has her own unique style and choice of instruments compared to Wise's tracks, it's quite easy to tell. Personally I think Wise generally has the better melodies while Fischer is really good at composing atmospheric tracks that helped define this game's soundtrack. I think her contribution was very important. Just hearing that harp/guitar instrument﻿ at the 10 seconds mark, you know it's from Fischer.
